com.solidfire.core.annotation

Annotation Type ConnectionType


  • @Documented
@Inherited
@Target(value={METHOD,CONSTRUCTOR,TYPE,PARAMETER})
@Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface ConnectionType
    Defines the type of connection this method can be run against from list: Cluster, Node. Attempting to run a Cluster-Only method against a Node connection (and vice versa) will result in an @see ApiException.
